Anyone complaining about the difficulty of this recipe is a complete moron. This is as easy as easy gets. The foil was fine. I guess the people complaining about the bombs slipping around their plates have never served ice cream before. Ice cream should not be served rock hard. It should sit out for 10-15 minutes before serving. Hello? This is a great recipe. Really easy and everyone raved. I would make this again in a heartbeat. The best part is they can be made a few days in advance. Just cutting them in half is presentation enough.

